Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:59.00,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}張りつめた空気が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}高まる鼓動広がってゆくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:11.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深く息吸い込んだなら
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:16.29,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}もう前しか見えないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰も代わる事出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.24,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私しか歩けない道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}その涙も全て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.42,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}輝きはじめる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:35.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}だから思いきり振り上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.13,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}手のひらに宿る{\fs26}POWER
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}迷わずにまっすぐに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.40,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}明日へと行くよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:47.17,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ほんのまばたきの瞬間に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}叶えるよ夢の{\fs26}STORY
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}儚くて遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.65,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}諦めないわいつも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.58,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}私だけの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:02.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)\fs26}BAMBOOBEAT{\r}を鳴らして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.89,0:01:59.00,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}喜歡著緊張的空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}興奮起來走向更廣闊的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:11.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}深呼一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:16.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只專注於眼前的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:21.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}誰都無法替代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.24,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只有我才能前進的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:27.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}連同那份淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:30.42,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}全部開始閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:35.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}因此將宿於手中的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:38.13,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}盡情揮揚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:40.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}果斷地  徑直地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:43.40,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}向著明天全力進發
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:47.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在轉瞬即逝之間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}實現那夢中的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:52.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}無論它多麼虛幻和遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.65,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}我也絕不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.58,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}和僅屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:03:02.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,300)}竹劍節奏響徹永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:24.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰も！　誰ひとり泣かさない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:30.31,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一気呵成　ファイナルチェンジ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:36.28,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:48.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.82,0:00:24.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}誰也！  誰也不能獨自哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.82,0:00:30.31,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}一氣呵成  Final Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.63,0:00:36.28,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:48.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超劍戰隊  Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴！就是現在！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.16,0:00:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連同普雷巴的份一起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！為什麼！你為什麼對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦囉嗦囉嗦！我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:36.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴機器人！參上！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴旋風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼  為什麼我們的敵人反而會救助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能親手打倒你們的  只有我而已！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  凜  你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.74,0:01:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.95,0:01:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.83,0:01:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個…了斷吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.22,0:01:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德！施奈德！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德——！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:15.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}第20話\NBraver和Shinaider
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  停
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.19,0:03:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  之前我也說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.17,0:03:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天週末開始我要出趟差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我考慮的結論是給你們放假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時隔甚久的休假啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近練習不斷嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個假期太貴重了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆別給我太放鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週一開始還要恢復魔鬼訓練！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:03:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安啦安啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:03:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮品給我帶甜點就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.05,0:04:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱不是旅行是出差啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.27,0:04:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.54,0:04:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明天要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:11.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  可能去買參考書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去做那種無聊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己練習  你也一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起來…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是！非常樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  明天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.92,0:04:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.04,0:04:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸從單位搞到了兩張影戲表演的票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話要不要一起去看？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼表演？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是太空13表演
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中超劍戰隊也會出來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.47,0:04:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎喲！約會？兩位？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真青春呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.41,0:04:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真親密呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就給你吧  要不要和誰去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和誰…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～我要幫家裡忙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～我很久都不在狀態了  都不知道怎麼辦囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.11,0:05:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.82,0:05:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君  有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:33.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GJ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:45.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  今天比平常洗得久了些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前說的爸爸的朋友明天就住過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.41,0:05:58.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多關照囉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.68,0:06:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概幾點？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家說是晚上來著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.59,0:06:09.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似還要先辦點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去鋪床了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.03,0:06:14.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空13…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別出演
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Red Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的超劍戰隊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡稱真·超劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.92,0:06:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要早睡才行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:11.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡不著…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:23.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先去表演舞台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路標在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:30.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.23,0:07:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是小珠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙戰隊  太空13
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空鐵拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.48,0:07:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空飛踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空手槍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們到這種地方來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.25,0:07:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來都是小孩子呢  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.92,0:08:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真投入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡太空13嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不上喜歡  不過也有在看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上來說還算有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是感覺成員太多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上敵人暗黑星雲12神將還要多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有緊張感不足等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成員這方面還一直沒有太好的角色詮釋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過我覺得CG場面處理得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.53,0:08:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為知道要好好地利用前作大受歡迎的元素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡也有很多炮彈射擊鏡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:43.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為描寫得比較詳細
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以看起來也很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭一次看到這麼能說的小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我記住！太空13！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:57.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！太空13的大勝利！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家鼓掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.08,0:09:04.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？出什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為打贏那種B級戰鬥員就有多了不起了  太空13
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:15.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是Death Armour
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了征服這個世界  現在復活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death Armour復活！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  不好啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:33.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個讓超劍戰隊都頭疼的Death Armour突然出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾回地獄吧！Death Armour！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會把這個世界交給你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份堅持能撐到多久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧！Death Friend們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:47.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空1號！拜託你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.98,0:09:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪人出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！有點黑暗的Death Friend們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.75,0:09:58.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感覺…好厲害的發展啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death Armour…又…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦！怎麼辦！太空1號深陷危機！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次世界終於要屬於我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布…布雷巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就來了！太空1號！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的旁邊…布雷巴經過了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:44.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待てよ！　邪悪な牙を剥いて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:50.34,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗤う　悪のデスアーマー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:56.18,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺が！　俺たちが許さない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:02.36,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危険上等　ブレイブチェンジ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.85,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心に正義　抱く者に
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:14.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仕えし剣を　いま空に　重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:26.61,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振り抜け　熱く　アトミック{\fn方正华隶_GBK\fs22}·{\r}ファイヤー{\fn方正华隶_GBK\fs22}·{\r}ブレード
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:32.89,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,おお　渦巻け　限りなく　サイクロン{\fn方正华隶_GBK\fs22}·{\r}ブレード
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美しい国　守る
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.45,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛と勇気の剣士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:44.32,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:55.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超剣戦隊ブレードブレイバー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.89,0:10:44.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}住手吧！  剝下邪惡的爪牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:50.34,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}嗤笑著  邪惡的Death Armour
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.65,0:10:56.18,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}我不能！  我們不能原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:02.36,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}危險最高  Brave Change!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:06.85,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}心懷正義之士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:14.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}侍奉之劍如今與天空相疊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:26.61,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}揮動熾熱的原子火焰劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:32.89,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}無限漩渦  Cyclone Brave
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}守護著美麗的國土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.45,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}兼備愛與勇氣的劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:44.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:55.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}超劍戰隊 Blade Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.21,0:10:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴鐵拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好吧？空間1號
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.11,0:10:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.96,0:10:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我上！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶！大家再大聲地為他們加油吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴  好棒！好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.80,0:11:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比部團活動的時候還要耀眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣！再大點聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  這邊的姐姐也大聲來加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不會為施奈德以外的人加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:30.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施奈德…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  姐姐也在加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也大聲的來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.31,0:11:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空火焰劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.35,0:11:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…輸了  太空1號  布雷巴紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！布雷巴紅  太空1號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場勝負就算你們贏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次就在劇場上見面吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布雷巴紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.79,0:12:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空間1號！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶～謝謝～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來參訪一下獲勝的二位吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:19.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄奮戰系列明年春天就要滿30週年了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以有準備特別企劃對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.36,0:12:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會重返超劍戰隊的新作電影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來要…出電影了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要準備好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太空13和超劍戰隊齊心協力\N和復活的Death Armour作戰的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然超劍戰隊是過去的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為這樣的電影適合家長和孩子一同觀看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  和TV版的角色都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:52.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍和黃  施奈德也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是  明年真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.48,0:12:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們現在稍微休息一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在後樂園  大家將與我進行熱情的握手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（後樂園是東京某大型遊樂場的名字）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.28,0:13:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？結果還是來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鞘你也不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.53,0:13:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且大家都來啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:24.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺一放鬆就會把學到的東西忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  我也總是在一考完試後就把單詞忘得一乾二淨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.11,0:13:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…那倒是很微妙的偏差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  在戰勝那個叫凱莉的傢伙之前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥是不會結束的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！小都都  Fight Guts Victory！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.47,0:13:44.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  段郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你還是不要說英語了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會想起那傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  小都都你這麼說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在勇次君進展不知道順不順利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:13:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說對方是小珠而這邊是勇次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  他們兩個是那樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我想完全不是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就不想在學校生活中留下些青澀回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而不是和渾身上下只有護具味道的傢伙混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…說合適倒也算合適…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又不像我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得勇次也沒什麼這方面的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.49,0:14:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說的話  應該是監護人的感覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小珠怎麼看勇次君呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀人…不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青梅竹馬…如今也不用這麼講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生…這是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次就是勇次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.94,0:14:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君  是越來越勇次君了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來是問答大賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是問答哦  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上去了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄奮戰～問答！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.82,0:15:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼～由我繼續來擔任主持人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個環節是從之前30年的故事系列中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提出各種各樣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快速搶答中獲得優勝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.72,0:15:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將能獲得…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限定版傳說中的英雄公仔豪華大放送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,限定…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.72,0:15:43.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼第一問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是今天的嘉賓Blade Braver提出的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡的大首領Death Armour喜歡的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  鈴木凜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海帶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:11.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二問
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Braver的制勝…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  川添珠姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.92,0:16:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原子火焰劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.53,0:16:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.17,0:16:32.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐們很有幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其餘各位也不要落後了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說小珠自然是很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:46.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木小姐  川添小姐都是80分
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的孩子們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…看來問題大賽姐姐們平手了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.17,0:17:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  勝負…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.80,0:17:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由兩位來演唱我們的英雄主題曲來見分曉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱…唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  由誰先來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌  唱歌  唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈴木凜  獻上施耐德之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱歌  唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了呢  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  鈴木小姐的得分是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來  有請川添珠姬小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川…川添珠姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.49,0:18:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演唱超劍戰隊Blade Braver…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠  握手會開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  猜謎大賽也打成了平手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有輸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.42,0:18:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  跟BRAVER好好握個手  我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.54,0:18:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的你要的話就請便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:55.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.25,0:18:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就收下吧  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.92,0:19:02.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客氣  那麼告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們去握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  還有攝影會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小珠  那個也要啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇次君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來打擾了  幫你拿行李吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布…布雷巴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了一跳嗎  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:00.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小珠啊  長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:04.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的朋友  小澤劍友會的代表小澤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不記得了嗎  小時候我們還見過幾面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.33,0:20:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.71,0:20:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前你還經常帶著年輕的弟子來我們道場研究武打場面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時真是給你添麻煩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:32.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小澤這次那個什麼…就是剛才小珠喜歡的那叫什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Braver啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  就是負責那個電影的動作畫面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.47,0:20:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拍攝期間就住在我們家了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊…您也先跟我說一下要來多少人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.99,0:20:52.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被子夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用操心  隨便睡睡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在外景這些還不是家常便飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:01.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Braver
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.87,0:21:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  不能讓保護和平的各位受了委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.94,0:21:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是懂事啊  小珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  明天就有拍攝  要來看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  珠姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒關係啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.80,0:21:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼可愛的小妹妹看著  這幫傢伙也得加把勁做了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  還能拜託你一件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:33.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個孩子雖然不是工作人員
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是相當的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次也一起過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.03,0:21:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能幫忙關照一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.29,0:21:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.46,0:21:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子也跟小珠一樣  是Braver的大粉絲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.78,0:21:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施耐德
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:06.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給您添麻煩了  請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是剛才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在哪裡見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}夕闇に  輝き出す  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}窓辺で素足のまま  夜を見上げて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眠れない 月明かり ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目の前を ちらついてく 昼間の私
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}自分だけ 空回りで もどかしいまま
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}目を閉じて  心の声  聞いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まだ知らない 私に出会いたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fs24}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}まばゆく  輝いてる  願いたち
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}この手の中 降りてきて 流れ星…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:22.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(300,0)}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.95,0:22:27.74,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}暮色中閃耀著的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.04,0:22:34.13,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}在窗邊光著腳丫  仰望著夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:02.22,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}唯有無法入眠的月光相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.09,0:23:10.09,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}眼前浮現出午時的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:17.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}只是徒勞得令人著急
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.39,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.68,0:23:25.43,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}閉上眼睛傾聽心中的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.72,0:23:32.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}依然無法得知  它想與我相見
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:35.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm Calling the STAR RISE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.52,0:23:40.27,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}光輝而耀眼的那小小心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:47.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}寄於手中  希望流星能為我實現…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.37,0:23:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Death Armour派出去刺殺Braver的孤高的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其名曰  竹劍超人Shinaider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:24:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其手中竹劍劈山破海  高樓大廈都能一切為二
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.26,0:24:03.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最強的敵人  雖說將布雷巴逼入危難
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.76,0:24:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是施耐德卻有著令人意外的傷感往事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.56,0:24:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回的超劍戰隊Blade Braver是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「參戰  破壞的竹劍  Shinaider」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是與之毫無相關的是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.41,0:24:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹劍少女將會播出「川添珠姬和鈴木凜」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
